  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Reporting to the Senior Project Manager, you will analyze VM props and fixtures requirements from clients with the production and designer team;</p>\n<p>· Continuously liaising with clients, design and production teams to ensure all design and technical details are followed;</p>\n<p>· Receive, fabricate and validate prototypes with clients;</p>\n<p>· Maintain control on project budget and timeline;</p>\n<p>· Ensure consistency and timely delivery of projects;</p>\n<p>· Attend on-site installation. Night work is required due to venue requirement;</p>\n<p>· Manage post installation maintenance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Holder of at least a Diploma or higher in a relevant discipline; Fresh Graduates are welcome to apply;</p>\n<p>· Strong interpersonal skills, able to work in a fast pace environment and multi-task;</p>\n<p>· Literate in MS Office. Knowledge in PhotoShop and Illustrator is good to have but not a must;</p>\n<p>· Must be able to work overtime / late night;</p>\n<p>· Strong written and oral communication skills;</p>\n<p>· Proactive, responsible, organized, able to work independently, and gives attention to detail;</p>\n<p>· Remuneration package shall be determined based on experience and qualifications.</p>",
